ource=N_triggered_bc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=n_shopbag_pd&amp;utm_channel=email_trig_ret_p&amp;utm_term=789708&amp;utm_content=20260324_nord\"><img width=\"320\" alt=\"Nordstrom\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;border:0;\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:34fecff9-6850-4db4-bd25-8aa181df042f\"></a></td><td width=\"50%\" style=\"padding:0;text-align:center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nordstromrack.com/?utm_source=N_triggered_bc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=n_shopbag_pd&amp;utm_channel=email_trig_ret_p&amp;utm_term=789708&amp;utm_content=20260324_rack\"><img width=\"320\" alt=\"Nordstrom Rack\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;border:0;\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:ce692f86-b2bf-4b6c-9c49-e914099dce14\"></a></td></tr></table></div><div class=\"acr-fragment acr-tmp-component\" data-tmp-component-id=\"text\" data-contenteditable=\"false\"><div class=\"text-container\"><p style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:16px;color:#000001;text-align:center;margin:0;padding:8px 25px;\"><a href=\"#\" data-nl-type=\"mirrorPage\" data-tracking-type=\"MIRROR_PAGE\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">View Online</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href=\"#\" data-nl-type=\"unsubscription\" data-tracking-type=\"OPT_OUT\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a></p><p style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:16px;color:#000000;text-align:left;margin:0;padding:8px 25px 0;\">&#8225;It can take a few days for recently issued Notes to appear in your Nordy Club account. Sign in to your Nordstrom account at <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/my-account/rewards?utm_source=N_triggered_bc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=n_shopbag_pd&amp;utm_channel=email_trig_ret_p&amp;utm_term=789708&amp;utm_content=20260324_creddisclaimer\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">nordstrom.com/myrewards</a> to see your most up-to-date Notes balance.<br><br>This is an advertising message from Nordstrom.<br><br>For complete Nordy Club program details, go to <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/nordy-club/terms-conditions?utm_source=N_triggered_bc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=n_shopbag_pd&amp;utm_channel=email_trig_ret_p&amp;utm_term=789708&amp;utm_content=20260324_nc_tcs\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">nordstrom.com/nordyterms</a>.<br><br>FREE SHIPPING. FREE RETURNS. This offer is only available for standard shipping on Nordstrom.com. Please visit Nordstromrack.com for details about their shipping and return policies.<br><br>NORDSTROM, 1600 Seventh Avenue, Suite 2600, Seattle, WA 98101<br><a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/customer-service/policy/privacy?utm_source=N_triggered_bc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=n_shopbag_pd&amp;utm_channel=email_trig_ret_p&amp;utm_term=789708&amp;utm_content=20260324_privacy\" style=\"color:#000001;text-decoration:underline;\">Nordstrom Privacy Policy</a><br><br>&#169;{%= formatDate(getCurrentZonedDateTime(), \"yyyy\") %} Nordstrom</p></div></div></div>",
